cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with video prediction using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes novel methods for feature learning, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of adversarial training is a common technique in generative models (cs.NE), and the paper also compares its results to published results using recurrent neural networks, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM).
